### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">إِنَّ ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنَ لَكُمْ عَدُوٌّ فَٱتَّخِذُوهُ عَدُوًّا ۚ إِنَّمَا يَدْعُوا۟ حِزْبَهُۥ لِيَكُونُوا۟ مِنْ أَصْحَـٰبِ ٱلسَّعِيرِ</span>

### English

Surely Satan is an enemy to you, so take him as an enemy. He only invites his followers to become inmates of the Blaze.